<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.285824>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Habitat of; a, C. pethiyagodai sp. nov. at high elevations of the Knuckles massif; b, C. liocephalus at mid elevations of Peak Wilderness (Photos: W. M. S. Botejue)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/285824/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.285818>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Holotype male (86.6 mm SVL) of Calotes pethiyagodai sp. nov., WHT 6211; a, dorsal head; b, lateral head; c, ventral head; d, pectoral scales: note greater snout scales and smaller occipital scales (a); longer snout (b); smaller mid gular scales (c), and not-enlarged pectoral scales (d), (Photos: M. De Silva)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/285818/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.285820>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A live adult male (86.6 mm SVL) of C. pethiyagodai sp. nov. (not collected) at 1300 m elevation of the Knuckles (Photo: V. Weeratunge)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/285820/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.285821>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Distribution map of C. liocephalus (red), and C. pethiyagodai sp. nov. (blue) based on examined specimens and personal observations made over the past 10 years." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/285821/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

